get.summary:
Clean JSON trips list for React.
Matches the old dashboard's getTripsList behavior with unified params.
Path: admin/trips/get-trips-list/{page_size}

put.summary:
Update a trip (partial updates supported via PUT/PATCH).
Prevents assigning a second Pending trip to the same driver.
PUT/PATCH: /api/admin/trips/{trip}

patch.summary:
Update a trip (partial updates supported via PUT/PATCH).
Prevents assigning a second Pending trip to the same driver.
PUT/PATCH: /api/admin/trips/{trip}
